(8, 4, '786312', 'Vonino Sirius QS 7.9 Inch Tablet with 3G 8GB Quad-Core 1.2Ghz - Silver', '<div class="panel-content">\n<div class="product-info">\n<div>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>2 Year Manufacturer Warranty</strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The Vonino Sirius QS tablet is a premium product of the range of tablets based on Android 4.2 Jelly Bean, developed by Google, which gives you the most pleasant experience of using a tablet.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The Vonino Sirius QS uses a Quad-Core processor running at 1.2GHz, 1GB of RAM and the Android 4.2 Jelly Bean operating system, all accessible via a 7.9 inch HD IPS multi touch capacitive display of high resolution.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The Vonino Sirius EVO QS can easily be used as your personal assistant by using business type applications or as a multimedia centre, due to the storage capacity of up to 36GB (using a micro SD card up to 32GB), a video Micro HDMI output and the embedded video cameras displayed on the front &ndash; 2.0MPx, and rear &ndash; 5.0MPx, but especially due to the IPS HD display resolution of 1024 x 768 pixels.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">A feature that highlights the Vonino Sirius QS is the Quad-Core Cortex A7 MT8389 processor. This platform is one of the most performing in terms of connection capacity, multimedia compatibility and low energy consumption. You have at your disposal a tablet equipped with one of the most efficient features of a must-have product: Quad-Core processor, 3G connectivity and Android 4.2 Jelly Bean operating system, all in one robust and slick product.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The main feature of tablets is that you are always in contact with the world. Vonino Sirius QS had the 3G module embedded with which you can connect to the internet, make or receive normal or video calls, wherever you are. Beside the 3G HSDPA+(21MBPS) connection Sirius QS incorporates the usual Wi-Fi connection; you can use two connections at the same time to create a Wi-Fi Hotspot to share your internet connection.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Because Vonino Sirius QS is a quality tablet it also offers you an embedded Bluetooth module. Through the Bluetooth connection you can synchronize the tablet with your personal computer or you can connect to it an external device such as a keyboard or headset.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Because the IPS-PRO HD type display with a capacity of 7.9 inch is big enough and offers a high resolution of 1024 x 768 pixels you can easily use Vonino Sirius QS to render videos and movies wherever you are, sharing the visual experience with those around you. This experience is that much more enjoyable thanks to the quality of the a high rendering quality of the IPS HD type display, which offers you a high quality rendered imagine, brightness and colour.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Vonino EGO QS incorporates 2 photo-video cameras placed on the front &ndash; 2.0mPx and on the back of the smartphone &ndash; 5.0mPx. Being compatible with all the video call applications offered by instant messaging services, such as Yahoo Messenger, Hangouts or Skype, these will allow you to interact in the most direct way with friends and business partners . At the same time, these offer you the possibility to direct your own videos.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">A tablet is all the more useful the more it manages to replace many devices. Vonino Sirius QS comes with an incorporated GPS module and digital compass, that allows you use it as a GPS navigator when you&rsquo;re in the car or walking on the street. You can get directions or search for points of interest located in the proximity of the place you are in.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We wish to offer users the best experience with these types of products, Vonino Sirius&nbsp; QS uses the most recent version of the operating system developed by Google, Android 4.2 Jelly Bean. Ever since the first version was launched, this operating system distinguished itself from competitors through the intuitive and easy to use interface and through the optimization of used resources. Jelly Bean version 4.2 comes with a redesigned user interface and a higher level of menus and main screens&nbsp; of this tablet. At the same time, Android 4.2 Jelly Bean was improved regarding the used resources while running programs thus increasing battery self-sufficiency.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>OS Google Android 4.2 Jelly Bean</li>\n<li>Processor Quad-Core MTK8389, Cortex A7 1.2GHz, PowerVR SGX 544 GPU</li>\n<li>1GB DDR3 SDRAM</li>\n<li>Built-in Storage: 8GB Nand-Flash</li>\n<li>3G built-in nano-SIM WCDMA, HSDPA, UMTS 2100Mhz; GSM, GPRS, EDGE 900/1800Mhz</li>\n<li>GPS built-in</li>\n<li>MicroSDHC Slot (Up to 32GB)</li>\n<li>Display: 7.9inch IPS Capacitive Multi-Touch 1024 x 768</li>\n<li>Wi-Fi 802.11b/g/n</li>\n<li>Bluetooth 4.0</li>\n<li>Micro USB Hi-Speed</li>\n<li>Back Camera: 5.0 Mpx Autofocus with Flash, Front Camera 2.0 Mpx</li>\n<li>Battery: Li-ion, 3.7V 4500mAh</li>\n<li>Dimensions: 200.2 x 7.4 x 134.8 mm</li>\n<li>Weight: 360g</li>\n<li>In the box: Vonino Sirius QS 7.9 Inch Tablet with 3G (8GB, Quad-Core, 1.2Ghz), power adaptor, micro-USB cable</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Technical Specifications:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Processor: Quad-Core MTK8389 Cortex A7 1,2GHz; PowerVR SGX 544 GPU</li>\n<li>Memory: 1GB DDR3 RAM; 8GB Nand-Flash; microSD card reader</li>\n<li>Display: 7.9inch IPS Capacitiv with auto-brightness, 1024x768</li>\n<li>Network: 3G WCDMA, HSDPA, UMTS 2100Mhz; 2G GSM, GPRS, EDGE 900/180Mhz</li>\n<li>GPS: Yes, built-in, GPS &amp; A-GPS</li>\n<li>Camera: 5.0mPx AF back-camera, 2.0mPx front-camera</li>\n<li>Wireless and port: Wi-Fi 802.11b/g/n; Buetooth 4.0; microUSB port(PC and charging)</li>\n<li>Battery: Li-Ion 3.7V 4500mAh</li>\n<li>Dimensions: WxDxH 200.2x7.4x134.8mm</li>\n<li>Weight: 360g</li>\n<li>Operating System: Google Android 4.2 Jelly Bean</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 219, 5, 3, '7ssfhgedv5_10925715-1398340230-797182.jpg', 0, 'sale', NULL, 'Vonino Sirius,Tablet,3G,Quad-Core,Silver', 1, '2015-01-12 02:33:09'),
(10, 4, '465213', 'Microsoft Surface Pro 2 10.6 Inch Tablet 128 GB', '<div class="panel-content">\n<div class="product-info">\n<div>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Enjoy incredible picture quality and Intel&reg; Core&trade; i5 power wherever you find yourself with the Microsoft Surface Pro 2 10.6&rdquo; Tablet. Complete with a full version of the touch optimised Windows 8.1 Pro operating system, the Surface Pro 2 puts your favourite apps and programs at your finger tips. Navigating your way around Windows 8 couldn''t be more intuitive. Simply touch the program you want from the Start screen and move around it by swiping, pinching or tapping the screen.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">With Live Tiles, Windows 8 keeps you updated with what matters to you. From news and emails to your social network, Live Tiles display instant updates from many applications without the need to open them. Windows 8 is Cloud ready, meaning all your documents, preferences and information can be securely backed up online. By simply logging in with an email address, you can easily access your files from any Windows device you find yourself using.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Unlike most tablets that are powered by micro-processors, the Surface Pro 2 is powered by a full-sized Intel&reg; Core&trade; i5-4200U processor. While the base clock speed of 1.6 GHz easily handles everyday tablet activities such as browsing the web and social networking, it can increase to an impressive 2.6 GHz when required. At this speed, the Surface Pro 2 is capable of much more intensive tasks such as online gaming and photo editing.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">4 GB of RAM allows the Surface Pro 2 to multitask with ease, so whether you''re streaming music while working or need multiple documents open at once, you can be confident there won''t be any slowdowns. A generous 128 GB hard drive provides ample storage for all your important files and folders. This can be upgraded thanks to the integrated microSD card adapter that makes backing up or storing large files simple.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The combination of 10-point multitouch screen and compact dimensions make the Surface Pro 2 a truly mobile alternative to full sized computer. Plus, thanks to an improved 1080p display, you can enjoy your films, games and images in beautiful, vivid 1080p HD wherever you are. Included is the Surface pen that lets you annotate documents, make notes or draw with ease, while connecting an optional touch or type cover provides the Surface Pro 2 with a full sized keyboard that''s perfect for typing long documents.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Although external programs are compatible, there''s a wealth of content available directly through the Windows Store. From the most popular games to news and catch-up TV, there''s certainly something you''ll love amongst the ever expanding library of apps. The magnesium case provides a smooth, durable surface that''s a delight to hold, while the integrated kick stand provides two standing positions that are perfect for watching films or typing.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Displaying in full high definition courtesy of the Intel HD graphics card, anything on the 10.6&rdquo; widescreen looks incredible. The USB 3.0 port provides a convenient connection for external media such as memory sticks and external hard drives, making it easy to back up and share your files. It also supports other USB devices such as mice and speakers.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">There are two cameras on board the Surface Pro 2; one front facing and one user facing. Perfect for video chatting and Skype, you can stay in contact with loved ones no matter where in the world you may find yourself. Make the most of the intuitive Windows 8.1 operating system regardless of location with the powerfully versatile Microsoft Surface Pro 2 10.6&rdquo; Tablet. - S.C.</p>\n<p><strong>Technical Specifications:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Software: Windows 8.1</li>\n<li>Exterior Dimensions: 275 x 173 x 13.5mm, Weight: 2lbs, Casing: VaporMg, Colour: Dark Titanium, Physical buttons: Volume, Power</li>\n<li>Storage: 128GB</li>\n<li>Display: Screen: 10.6 in, Resolution: 1920 x 1080, Aspect Ratio: 16:9 (widescreen), Touch: 10-point multi-touch, Durable display</li>\n<li>CPU and Wireless: 4th generation Intel Core &trade; i5 Processor, TPM Chip for enterprise security, Wireless: Wi-Fi (802.11a/b/g/n), Bluetooth 4.0 Low Energy technology</li>\n<li>Battery Life: 7-15 days idle life, Charges in 2-4 hours with included power supply</li>\n<li>Cameras, Video and Audio: Two 720p HD cameras, front and rear-facing, Microphone, Stereo speakers</li>\n<li>Ports: Full-size USB 3.0, microSD card reader, Headset jack, HD video out port, Cover port</li>\n<li>Sensors: Ambient light sensor, Accelerometer, Gyroscope, Magnetometer</li>\n<li>In the box: Surface Pro 2 with Windows 8.1 Pro, 48W power supply, Quickstart guide, Safety and warranty documents, Surface Pen</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 1004.95, 900, 0, 'pykksbt7ud_10925290-1395068394-709891.jpg', 1, 'sale', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bLUPXHxIwdk', 'Microsoft Surface,Tablet,128 GB,Windows', 1, '2015-01-09 10:15:11'),
(14, 4, '985321', 'Samsung Galaxy Tab 3 WiFi 10.1 Inch Tablet 16 GB - White', '<div class="panel-content">\n<div class="product-info">\n<div>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The Samsung Galaxy Tab 3 10.1" is everything you and your family want in a device. From its sophisticated design, which boasts a stunning 10.1 WXGA display, to the enhanced multimedia experience, it is the ultimate companion. Other cool features include Dolby Digital Plus audio, Samsung Hub service and Story Album. So, whether you are planning to stay at home or venture outdoors, this tablet is the perfect partner and will always have something to keep you entertained.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The new GALAXY Tab 3 10.1" offers a sleek design with a lighter and slimmer form while still providing a gloriously large 10.1" screen. You''ll have a comfortable grip while still enjoying the majestic view. 10.1" WXGA resolution (1280 x 800, 149PPI) guarantees a crisp and clear, incredibly sharp delivery of all your hi-resolution photos and videos.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">If music is your passion, built in Sound Alive audio enhancer will truly be a music to your ear. Enjoy deeper drum and extended tinge when listening to your favouritmusic. Moreover, you''ll get an immersing audio experience from all your videos with Dolby Surround.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Find your favourite show easily and get the lists of Top pick&rsquo;s TV show recommended from the guide. Easily control your TV by using the remote control function. GALAXY Tab3 10.1" integrates 2.4GHz / 5GHz Channel and accelerates 2 times faster data transfer speed (143Mbps) providing you environment for fast content share.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Whether resting on the couch, playing in the den or reading e-books to your children in bed, enjoy a stimu-lating world of digial contents of fun and relaxed sharing. Buy or rent movies from Video Hub, your personal video store concierge. With progressive 