(15, 4, '876314', 'Sony Xperia Tablet Z 10.1 Inch Full HD 4G Tablet 16 GB', '<div class="panel-content">\n<div class="product-info">\n<div>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Think about the sharpest, most vivid TV picture. Now imagine it on a tablet. Xperia Tablet Z delivers the kind of immersive viewing you&rsquo;d normally only get with an HDTV. Created by the people behind BRAVIA&reg; TVs, Xperia Tablet Z brings Sony&rsquo;s expertise to an HD tablet. The brilliant 10.1&rdquo; Reality Display is powered by Mobile BRAVIA&reg; Engine 2, which enhances the clarity and richness of every image. This HD tablet boasts the fullest colour display, too. For bluer blues, greener greens and seriously killer sunsets. With Xperia Tablet Z you meet a world so vivid, everything else pales in comparison.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">At just 6.9 mm and weighing under 500 grams, Xperia&trade; Tablet Z is beautifully light for a 10.1&rdquo; tablet. But don&rsquo;t let the feel of it fool you. This premium tablet may be slim and light, but it&rsquo;s no lightweight! Sony OmniBalance design focuses on creating balance and symmetry in all directions. Xperia&trade; Tablet Z has subtly rounded edges and a smooth, reflective glass surface.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The latest Snapdragon&trade; S4 Pro asynchronous quad core processor gives you breathtaking speed and jaw-dropping graphics. Powerful computing, without lightning-speed battery drain. This ultra-light Android tablet is water-resistant, with a super-strong glass display. Whether you&rsquo;re surfing poolside or scrolling through a recipe with wet fingers, Xperia&trade; Tablet Z can take it.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Xperia Tablet Z brings you more than a tablet experience. We&rsquo;ve used our broad expertise in consumer electronics to design an Android tablet that&rsquo;s ready for new levels of connection. Xperia Tablet Z can control other devices, share content between screens and act as the perfect companion to your TV experience. So you can change the channels on your TV while you tweet. Want to see your memories on the big screen? Choose a photo on your HD tablet, then share it to the TV with One-touch mirroring. No cables, no buttons, no confusion. Just the content you want, wherever you want it. And if you want it on the go? Xperia Tablet Z keeps everything coming at top speed via LTE/4G.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Get ready for viewing gone truly vivid. A design so slim and light, you&rsquo;d never guess it was built for unparalleled power and performance. Xperia Tablet Z is the HD tablet from Sony that throws out the need for compromise. Watch the most colourful scenes, tune into the highest quality sound, take the most stunning pictures and connect your home in ways you&rsquo;ve always wanted.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">All the games, films, music and books you could want. Xperia Tablet Z is bursting with entertainment possibilities, ready for download or streaming. Sony Entertainment Network comes pre-loaded, putting thousands of music tracks and films at your fingertips. Or tap into Google Play for over 600,000 Android apps. However you like to spend your time, Xperia Tablet Z is built to entertain. Made your pick? Then sit back and get ready for the most immersive entertainment experience. Xperia Tablet Z doesn&rsquo;t just bring you top entertainment &ndash; it delivers it via a brilliant display, the sharpest graphics and the best tablet sound.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Films on a tablet have never been more immersive. Xperia&trade; Tablet Z gives a wide-screen cinema experience on the most vivid display imaginable. Experience visually stunning graphics in even the most advanced games. Xperia&trade; Tablet Z is Playstation Certified and comes with a graphic processor 2 times faster than the previous snapdragon GPU. Listen to music as it was meant to be played. Sony&rsquo;s audio expertise brings 3D surround sound technology and Clear Audio+. For richer sound that&rsquo;s closer to the real thing. - S.C.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Android&trade; 4.1 (Jelly Bean)</li>\n<li>Quad core 1.5 GHz Snapdragon S4 Pro processor</li>\n<li>Android Apps available on Google Play&trade;</li>\n<li>microSD card slot</li>\n<li>16GB capacity</li>\n<li>4G connectivity</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Technical Specifications:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>On the inside: Google Android 4.3 (Jelly Bean), 1.5 GHz Qualcomm APQ8064+MDM9215M Quad Core, Adreno 320</li>\n<li>Camera: 8.1 Megapixels, 16x Digital zoom, Front-facing camera (2.2 MP 1080p)</li>\n<li>Display: 10.1 inches TFT, 16,777,216 colours, 1920x1200 pixels</li>\n<li>Durability: Water-resistant (IP55 and IP57) [1], Dust-resistant (IP55) [1]</li>\n<li>Weight: 495 grams</li>\n<li>Dimensions: 172 x 266 x 6.9 mm</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 515.99, 0, 3, 'uzksn3bzdd_10925307-1395068394-712395.jpg', 0, 'sale', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BhvE_xNeRto', 'Sony Xperia,Sony,tablet,HD,4G,16 GB', 1, '2015-01-09 10:19:04'),
(17, 4, '988422', 'Apple iPad mini 3 Wi-Fi 16GB - Gold', '<div class="panel-content">\n<div class="product-info">\n<div>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">With iOS 8 and Touch ID security, the Apple iPad mini 3 offers the latest Apple advancements in a highly compact package.<br /><br /><strong>mini</strong><br /><br />At a mere 341 grams the mini is the lightest iPad available. It can be carried anywhere, and thanks to the quality aluminium case, can stand up to everyday use.<br /><br />Despite its compact size, the mini delivers a full iPad experience. The 7.9&rdquo; Retina Display is perfectly sized to give you a complete view of your digital content and features a higher-than-HD resolution, so you can enjoy videos, photos and more in beautiful detail.<br /><br />Along with fast processing that ensures apps run at their best, the A7 processor delivers impressive graphics that take mobile gaming to the next level, so you can enjoy the best of your favourite touchscreen games wherever you are.<br /><br /><strong>iOS 8</strong><br /><br />The iPad mini comes preinstalled with iOS 8. Featuring a colourful new design, iCloud integration and tons of new features including the ability to send and receive text messages directly from the tablet when paired with an iPhone, it takes the iOS formula you know and makes it better.<br /><br />There are now well over a million apps available from the App Store, so whatever you''re into, the iPad mini has something you''ll love.<br /><strong><br />Fingerprint scanner</strong><br /><br />Keeping your private information private is quick and easy thanks to the new Touch ID fingerprint scanner - simply swipe your finger over the sensor embedded in the Home button to unlock your account.<br /><br />Great features<br /><br />Connecting and charging are easier than ever with the Lightning connector.&nbsp; A Lightning to USB cable is supplied, so you can charge and share data with ease.<br /><br />Staying in touch with far-away friends i