(23, 6, '884421', 'Apple iPod Touch 16GB (5th Gen) - Blue', '<div class="panel-content">\n<div class="product-info">\n<div>\n<p>The ultra-slim, ultra-light iPod touch comes in fresh colours, and rocks the incredible new Apple EarPods. More screen means more music, messages, websites and games. And it all looks stunning on the Retina display. Make every shot your best with advanced optics, tap to focus and LED flash. And shoot video in 1080p HD.</p>\n<p>Send unlimited texts with iMessage over Wi-Fi. See your friend&rsquo;s every expression with a FaceTime video call. Check your email with Mail, and browse the web with Safari. And iOS 6 adds to the mix with Siri, Facebook integration, Maps, Passbook and more.</p>\n<p><strong>In the Box:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>iPod touch (5th generation)</li>\n<li>iPod touch loop</li>\n<li>Apple EarPods</li>\n<li>Lightning to USB Cable</li>\n<li>Quick Start Guide</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>6-mm ultra-thin design</li>\n<li>4-inch Multi-Touch Retina display</li>\n<li>Wi-Fi enabled, Bluetooth 4.0</li>\n<li>A5 chip for faster processing</li>\n<li>1080p HD video recording</li>\n<li>5-megapixel iSight camera</li>\n<li>iTunes and the App Store, Siri, iMessage</li>\n<li>FaceTime, Game Center, email, Safari web browser</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 220.99, 0, 0, 'dtibguu24f_10977989-1405083199-920893.jpg', 0, NULL, NULL, 'Apple,Apple iPod,iPod,16GB', 1, '2015-01-10 16:35:50'),
(24, 6, '454534', 'Philips GoGEAR SoundDot SA5DOT02BN/12 MP3 Player', '<div class="panel-content">\n<div class="product-info">\n<div>\n<p>Big on fun and incredibly small in size. The Philips GoGEAR SA5DOT02BN/12 GoGEAR SoundDot MP3 Player boasts a 2GB capacity, and features a built-in clip for convenient, hands-free use. Providing you with six hours of music playback, the device connects via direct USB to your computer to charge, with no need for cables. Meanwhile, the quick charge function will allow you to achieve 60 minutes of play in just six minutes.</p>\n<p>With sound and LED indicators for charging and easy navigation, the MP3 player also comes with the Philips Songbird program, which is a powerful music management system that lets you discover new artists and music styles directly in the program through music and media stores, services and website, whilst allowing you to play your own library and media from the internet and seamlessly sync all of it from your PC to your Philips GoGear. A built-in clip lets you wear it like an accessory, while LED and sound indicators ensure easy navigation. FastCharge offers quick charging.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fullsound&trade; brings your music to life</li>\n<li>Small, colorful and stylish like a fashion accessory</li>\n<li>Built-in clip for convenient and hands-free use</li>\n<li>Enjoy up to 6 hours of music playback</li>\n<li>Quick 6-minute charge for 60 minutes of play</li>\n<li>Songbird: One simple program to manage music and videos</li>\n<li>2GB memory</li>\n<li>Stores up to 500 songs</li>\n<li>USB port</li>\n<li>Rechargeable, built-in battery</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 19.5, 0, 2, 'forwn46a8u_10949050-1399018471-545803.jpg', 0, NULL, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MsuYCBPyjPY', 'Philips,MP3 Player,GoGEAR,SoundDot', 1, '2015-01-12 02:33:09'),
(25, 7, '669003', 'Sony AS100VR Full HD Action Camera Bundle with Live View Wrist Watch', '<div class="panel-content">\n<div class="product-info">\n<div>\n<p>The HDR-AS100V Action Cam&rsquo;s image quality, advanced blur reduction and simultaneous multi-angle shooting ensures great footage. Its rugged splashproof design delivers great versatility.</p>\n<p>With a class-leading 50Mbps recording capability, Sony&rsquo;s advanced BIONZ X image processor, a specially-designed ZEISS lens and more, the HDR-AS100V lets you bring home gorgeous footage under any conditions. Advanced SteadyShot image stabilisation compensates for various kinds of blur, especially the rapid vibrations caused by a motorised vehicle, like a motocross bike or snowmobile.</p>\n<p>One jaw-dropping frame at a time is the best way to re-live amazing action. With category-leading 120fps + 240fps speed, you can freeze-frame + edit with total control. These frame rates also record audio, so your slo-mo scenes feel authentic.</p>\n<p>Take on harsh, dusty and dry environments with the tough SPK-AS2 case (included), which seals out grit and dust. And in a stroke of design ingenuity, Action Cam&rsquo;s glossy white finish reflects sunlight - keeping it cool for peak performance.</p>\n<p>Whether you&rsquo;re riding in the rain or carving the slopes, the splashproof design means no further protection is needed. And attach the supplied tripod adapter directly to the Action Cam body to easily connect other accessories. Surfing, kayaking and more - you&rsquo;ll get amazing footage when you bring along the Action Cam encased in its waterproof case SPK-AS2 (supplied), good down to five metres.</p>\n<p>Manage up to five cameras using the optional Live View Remote. Check viewing angles on the wrist-mounted colour monitor at a glance, start/stop recording on five cameras at once, and changes settings simultaneously on all units. No cables needed, thanks to built-in Wi-Fi.</p>\n<p><strong>In the Box:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Sony AS100VR Action Camera</li>\n<li>Live View Wrist Watch</li>\n<li>Adhesive plate</li>\n<li>Underwater housing</li>\n<li>Micro-USB cable</li>\n<li>Operating guide</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Pro XAVC S format - Sony&rsquo;s professional grade codec is now available in consumer cameras to show stunning footage in your living room.</li>\n<li>Exmor R CMOS sensor - A cutting-edge sensor packs in more pixels for low-noise shooting in dark settings, using incident light alone.</li>\n<li>BIONZ X Processor - Blazing 50Mbps recording, paired with SteadyShot image stabilisation, means fast action with smooth motion - for high-quality HD footage.</li>\n<li>Wide-angle ZEISS Tessar lens - A panoramic 170&deg; viewing angle provides the perfect way to capture expansive ski slopes and winding mountain trails.</li>\n<li>Advanced SteadyShot image stabilisation.</li>\n<li>Category-leading 120fps + 240fps speed.</li>\n<li>Dustproof, splashproof, shockproof and waterproof down to 5m with the supplied SPK-AS2 case</li>\n<li>Live View Remote lets you control up to five cameras using the wrist-mounted colour monitor</li>\n<li>Transfer files and link devices with just a tap. With the simplicity of NFC, you only need to touch devices to connect. And no complex setup is required when connecting to Android smartphones and tablets</li>\n<li>Sony&rsquo;s PlayMemories Home offers a number of features that let you put together an impressive and unique final cut you&rsquo;ll be proud to share. Video Merge enables you to combine up to four views of action in one screen and GPS Data Overlay shows GPS data stored in Action Cam to display your route and speedometer readings on screen.</li>\n<li>Two pro-level functions make this camcorder the choice for serious filmmakers. The new Neutral colour mode allows precise adjustments. And&mdash;for easier multiple-camera recording/editing&mdash;time code and user bit stamp frames with time and scene data.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Technical Specifications:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>18.9MP Exmor R&trade; CMOS sensor</li>\n<li>Advanced Bionz X processor</li>\n<li>ZEISS ultra-wide (170&deg;) Tessar lens</li>\n<li>Splash-proof design</li>\n<li>Simple sharing and control with Wi-Fi and NFC One-touch</li>\n<li>Lens Type - Carl Zeiss&reg; Tessar&reg; Lens</li>\n<li>Sensor Type - 1/2.3&rdquo; (7.76mm) back-illuminated Exmor&reg; R CMOS Sensor</li>\n<li>Waterproof - Yes(In use with Waterproof Case (SPK-AS2))</li>\n<li>Dustproof - Yes(In use with Waterproof Case (SPK-AS2))</li>\n<li>Shockproof - Yes(In use with Waterproof Case (SPK-AS2))</li>\n<li>Input and Output Terminals - Multi/Micro USB Terminal, Microphone Input, Micro HDMI output (sold separately), Memory Card Slot, Composite Video Out</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 363.99, 0, 2, 'v7mt545odg_10954137-1402326463-401733.jpg', 1, 'new', NULL, 'Sony,Full HD,Camera,AS100VR,Wi-Fi,GPS,Live', 1, '2015-01-10 16:59:32'),
(26, 7, '611113', 'Fujifilm FinePix S1 Bridge Camera (WiFi, Weather Resistant) - Black', '<div class="panel-content">\n<div class="product-info">\n<div>\n<p>The Fujifilm FinePix S1 is the world''s first weather resistant camera in its class. Shoot where you want, when you want without the worries about the weather, season or general shooting environment. The world''s first weather resistant (water resistant and dust resistant ) structure in its class. The lens-body integrated design and sealing on approx. 70 areas are designed to allow field photography without typical worries about the weather, season or general shooting environment.</p>\n<p>The FinePix S1 boasts a high-resolution (920K-dot) electronic view-finder, making it easier to frame subjects and check focus in bright daylight conditions.The bright EVF accommodates a traditional shooting style, making it easy to steady the camera, even when shooting with the 50x zoom fully extended. The 3" LCD monitor is perfect for high angle shots that look out over a crowd of people to low angle shots that capture flowers close to the ground, you can take photos and movies from a wide variety of positions, comfortably.</p>\n<p>The 50x optical zoom with Optical Image Stabilisation means you''ll never miss a shot with the super fast 50x optical zoom wide angle lens. Vast zoom range from 24mm wide-angle to 1200mm super-telephoto offers the advanced features and flexibility of a DSLR without the weight and hassle of interchangeable lenses. 3.0-stop image stabilisation to reduce blurring and produce excellent results from wide angle to telephoto.</p>\n<p>Fujifilm''s super resolution technology offers an incredible 100x Intelligent Digital Zoom. Newly developed image processing software produces excellent quality results throughout the whole image, right to the edges of the frame. Distant subjects are captured in crisp detail even when at the full zoom. The FinePix S1''s smooth, high-speed, responsive performance allows you to capture fast moving subjects easily. Fujifilm has ensured excellent performance by introducing parallel processing via a newly developed multi CPU processor. This is compatible with UHS-1 SD cards and data is written at high speeds ensuring immediate results.</p>\n<p>Record full HD movies with 5-axis image stabilisation. Shoot movies easily with Movie scene recognition and the newly-developed 5-Axis Image Stabilisation. The FinePix S1 allows you to share images wirelessly via PC, tablet or smartphone and to control your camera via smartphone with the free Fujifilm Camera Remote app. Enjoy artistic expressions easily with Advanced Filters and Interval Shooting plus a whole host of preset shooting modes.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Weather resistant (water resistant and dust resistant)</li>\n<li>Electronic viewfinder and eye sensor</li>\n<li>Side lever and instant zoom-out button</li>\n<li>Optical Zoom - 50 x (24mm - 1200mm)</li>\n<li>LCD Monitor - 3" (920K-dot)</li>\n<li>ISO - 12900</li>\n<li>Continuous Shooting - 10fps (max 9 frames</li>\n<li>16M BSI-CMOS</li>\n<li>Intelligent Digital Zoom up to 100x (2400mm)</li>\n<li>Optical image stabilisation</li>\n<li>920K-dot viewfinder</li>\n<li>Advanced filters</li>\n<li>Lithium-ion rechargable battery</li>\n<li>0.14 second auto focus</li>\n<li>Full manual controls</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 480.99, 420, 2, 'oxo9mqr9p1_10934037-1396971503-706504.jpg', 1, 'sale', NULL, 'Fujifilm,Camera,WiFi,Weather Resistant', 1, '2015-01-10 17:45:45'),
(27, 7, '654300', 'Fujifilm FinePix S9200 Bridge Camera (50x Optical Zoom) - Red', '<p>The Fujifilm S9200 Bridge Camera features a Fujinon 50x ultra-long optical zoom lens to seamlessly cover an enormous focal range with no need to ever change lenses. The S9200 captures 16-megapixel photos and Full HD movies, with a 16M BSI-CMOS makes even dark scenes bright for high-quality images.</p>\n<div class="panel-content">\n<div class="product-info">\n<div>\n<p>Fujinon zoom lenses with fast apertures of f/2.9 to f/6.5 With 17 elements in 12 groups, the lens combines aspherical and ED elements to good effect for reduced aberration and superior image quality. With Super-Macro Mode capturing subjects as close as 1cm from the lens, the FinePix S9400W, S9200 seamlessly covers an enormous focal range with no need to ever change lenses.</p>\n<p>You can easily transfer images wirelessly from the FinePix S9200 to your smartphone or tablet after installing the free FUJIFILM Camera Application app. There are no troublesome ID and password settings; just press the MENU button of the back of the camera and then add the images instantly to your blog or share them with friends on your social networking site. You can also use the FinePix S9200''s built-in Wi-Fi to save your photos to your PC.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fujinon 50x Optical Zoom (24mm-1200mm) and Super Macro</li>\n<li>Powerful Optical Image Stabilization - Lens shift image stabilization ensures that even hand-held shots are free from blur.</li>\n<li>100x Intelligent Digital Zoom - Fujifilm''s proprietary super resolution technology offers an overwhelming 100x Intelligent Digital Zoom in.</li>\n<li>Movie functions - Full HD Movie (1080p / 60 fps)</li>\n<li>Continuous Shooting 10 fps at full resolution</li>\n<li>Quick response</li>\n<li>Side-lever zoom control</li>\n<li>Electronic viewfinder</li>\n<li>Easy-to hold grip</li>\n<li>6 Scene SR AUTO - Modes: Portrait, landscape, night, macro, night portrait, backlit portrait</li>\n<li>Versatile shooting modes and mode dials</li>\n<li>Easy web uploading to YouTube&trade; and Facebook via MyFinePix Studio</li>\n<li>Art filters - toy camera, miniature, pop colour, soft focus, cross screen, partial colour, high-key, low-key, dynamic tone, fish-eye</li>\n<li>Motion panorama 360 - Just sweep the camera right-left or up-down to shoot giant panoramas up to 360&deg;. When you view the panorama playing back on your camera or personal computer, you can enjoy a seamless panorama image with both ends stitched together to create a &ldquo;cylinder&rdquo; view.</li>\n<li>Dynamic Range (HDR)</li>\n<li>Zoom Bracketing Mode</li>\n<li>Natural Light &amp; with Flash</li>\n<li>Face Tracking Auto Focus</li>\n<li>Face Detection</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 297.75, 0, 2, 'pu2r3b3k4q_10934036-1397031257-557160.jpg', 0, 'hot', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k7ggau4PVJ8', 'Fujifilm,camera,Optical Zoom,50x,Red,CMOS Sensor', 1, '2015-01-10 17:52:20'),
(28, 7, '566631', 'Fujifilm FinePix XP70 Outdoor Digital Camera (16MP, 5x Optical Zoom) - Blue', '<div class="panel-content">\n<div class="product-info">\n<div>\n<p>Take the Fujifilm FinePix XP70 anywhere - it''s waterproof, shockproof, freezeproof and dustproof and the LCD works in bright sunlight. Take the XP70 anywhere - it''s waterproof, shockproof, freezeproof and dustproof and the LCD works in bright sunlight. Action Camera mode is perfect for recording HD movie footage whilst enjoying outdoor sports.</p>\n<p>In Action Camera mode, the LCD monitor automatically turns off when you start to shoot movies, thereby supporting energy-saving shooting. Movies can be recorded whilst your hands are full by fixing the camera to your body or sports equipment. Capture even more of the action by using the 18mm wide-angle lens converter (Action Camera Lens ACL-XP70).</p>\n<p>Capture high resolution, great quality photos. The XP70 has a 16-megapixel CMOS sensor with a 5x optical zoom and Optical Image Stabilisation. Enjoy artistic expressions easily with Advanced Filters plus a whole host of preset shooting modes. Share your high quality images on the spot by installing the free Fujifilm Camera Application app on your smartphone or tablet.</p>\n<p>The dedicated "Burst mode button" lets you instantly switch into continuous shooting mode, making it easy to capture exactly the moment or expression that you''re shooting for. Characterised by high-speed processing, the CMOS sensor enables continuous shooting at up to 10 frames/sec. (max. 10 frames) or ultra-high-speed bursts at a maximum 60 frames/sec.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>4-Way Protection - Waterproof to 20ft (IPX8) , shockprooof to 5ft, freezeproof to -10&deg;C, dustproof (IP6X)</li>\n<li>Bright and clear 2.7" LCD monitor with anti-reflective coating for excellent visibility</li>\n<li>Stable one-handed shooting - The grip on the front of the camera and the thumb rest on the back of the camera ensure users have a firm grasp of the camera to aid one-handed shooting.</li>\n<li>Safe double-lock mechanism - The extra safe double-locking system prevents the lid from accidentally being opened.</li>\n<li>"Burst Mode Button" for responsive, hassle-free shooting - Capture the action quickly and surely with continuous shooting toggle button.</li>\n<li>Full HD movie (1080i / 60 fps) with dedicated movie record button (1920 x 1080 full HD)</li>\n<li>16-megapixel CMOS sensor with a 5x optical zoom and Optical Image Stabilisation</li>\n<li>28mm wide angle, 5x optical zoom lens with 10x Intelligent Digital Zoom</li>\n<li>Art Filters - Pop colour, toy camera, miniature, soft focus, partial colour, cross screen, high-key, low-key, dynamic tone, fish-eye</li>\n<li>Motion Panorama 360</li>\n<li>Easy web uploading to YouTube&trade; and Facebook via MyFinePix Studio</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 206, 0, 10, 'ld5oakox46_10934028-1396971503-705346.jpg', 0, NULL, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Kh5VhCenYyA', 'Fujifilm,FinePix,Digital Camera,Digital,Camera,16MP,Optical Zoom', 1, '2015-01-12 21:09:13'),
(29, 5, 'panda234543', 'Panda 2014 Global Protection (3 Users/ License, 1 Year)', '<div class="panel-content">\n<div class="product-info">\n<div>\n<p>Panda 2014 Global Protection is designed to let you enjoy life online. This software provides maximum protection for smartphones (Android), tablets (Android), PCs and Macs. It protects your data regardless of what device you''re using.</p>\n<p>With the PC recovery system you can start your computer in safe mode and cure it from viruses in emergencies or critical scenarios. You can even share this with other people to help them clean their computers.</p>\n<p>Protect your PC or Mac from all sorts of known and unknown threats. Install it to protect your family from inappropriate content, while also shielding your documents and confidential data. With Panda Internet Security 2014 you can ensure your private files are safe. Protect your family from online fraud, phishing, identity theft and other threats.</p>\n<p>If your computer is running slow, then Panda Global Protection 2014 can be used to optimise and update your computer. Panda Global Protection 2014 can protect the latest Macs, iPad, iPhone and iPod touch devices when connected.</p>\n<p>Panda Global Protection 2014 will ensure you stay safe against any type of internet threats on your tablets and smartphones. Browse the web, bank and shop online or stay connected on social media with full protection.</p>\n<p>Installing security software has never been easier, Panda is light, fast and quick to install. Panda Global Protection 2014 is a modern and intuitive user experience just like the latest operating systems. - A.D. </p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Panda Global Protection 2014 (3 Users/license for 1 year)</li>\n<li>Advanced protection for all your devices</li>\n<li>Panda Security Cloud Technology offers a new protection model based on a user community where everyone contributes. Your computer will always be updated and protected. Additionally, your PC won''t limit detection capabilities as Panda''s huge virus detection database is located on the Internet (in the Cloud)</li>\n<li>Protection against spyware, phishing (online fraud), rootkits (stealth techniques) and banker Trojans.</li>\n<li>Real-time protection</li>\n<li>New Web Filter for safe Web browsing</li>\n<li>Complete protection against known and unknown virus attacks</li>\n<li>Vaccinate your USB flash drives against infections</li>\n<li>Firewall. Block intruders and hackers, even on your wireless network</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Technical Specifications:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Operating System: Windows 8 (32-bit and 64-bit), Windows 7 (32-bit and 64-bit), Windows Vista (32-bit and 64-bit), Windows XP (32-bit only), Android 2.2 or later</li>\n<li>Technical Requirements: Processor: Pentium 300 MHz or faster, RAM: 128 MB (1 GB recommended), Hard Disk: 265 MB free space, MS Internet Explorer 6.0</li>\n<li>Supported Browser: Microsoft Internet Explorer 6.0 or higher, Mozilla Firefox 2 or higher, Google Chrome</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 80, NULL, 0, '2y0smqfbws_10868008-1385142685-583797.jpg', 0, NULL, NULL, 'Panda 2014,Global Protection', 1, '2015-01-10 18:01:08');
