(30, 5, '450000', 'Microsoft Office For Mac Home and Business 2011 - License Card, 1 User', '<div class="panel-content">\n<div class="product-info">\n<div>\n<p>Office for Mac Home and Business is designed and licensed for more advanced personal use, home-based work and small businesses. Work when and where you want from any computer with a browser and the Office Web Apps. And communicate and share with virtually anyone with the world&rsquo;s most reliable Office for Windows compatibility.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Word</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>In the new Read Mode, text reflows automatically in columns for easier on-screen reading</li>\n<li>Fewer menus means more focus on your content - see only the tools you need, when you need them</li>\n<li>Open a PDF in Word, and edit content just as if you created it in Word</li>\n<li>Show your style by using Word templates in more than 40 categories</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Excel</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Each workbook has its own window, making it easier to work on two workbooks - or two monitors - at once</li>\n<li>New functions in the math and trig, statistical, engineering date and time, lookup and reference, logical, and text function categories</li>\n<li>The new Recommended Charts button lets you pick from a variety of charts that are right for you data</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>PowerPoint</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Presenter View allows you to see your notes on your monitor while the audience only sees the slide</li>\n<li>Smart Guides automatically appear when your objects are close to even, and tell you when objects are spaced evenly</li>\n<li>Support for more multimedia formats, such as .mp4 and .mov, more high-definition content, and more built-in codecs</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Outlook</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Synchronise multiple email accounts from services such as Hotmail, Gmail, or just about any other provider</li>\n<li>Easily import your email, contacts and to-do list from Outlook for Windows</li>\n<li>The new ribbon helps you find the commands that you already know how to use in an intuitive, easy-to-use interface</li>\n<li>Assign colour-coded categories to messages, contacts and other items to help you tell at glance which items deserve your attention</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>System Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Required Processor - A Mac computer with an Intel processor</li>\n<li>Required Operating System - Mac OS X version 10.5.8 or later</li>\n<li>Recommended Memory - 1GB of RAM recommended</li>\n<li>Required Media Drive - DVD drive or connection to a local area network (if installing over a network)</li>\n<li>Other System Requirements - HFS+ hard disk format (also known as Mac OS Extended or HFS Plus) Certain online functionality requires a Microsoft account. Certain features require Internet access (fees may apply). Exchange support in Outlook 2011 requires connectivity to Microsoft Exchange 2007 SP1 RU4 or later. Access to files stored on a SharePoint server requires connectivity to Microsoft Office SharePoint Server 2007 or later. Co-authoring requires SharePoint 2010 or a Microsoft account.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 246, NULL, 12, 'a7sym8ztza_10978071-1405093952-227047.jpg', 0, 'new', NULL, 'Microsoft Office,Business 2011,licence,Mac,Microsoft,Office', 1, '2015-01-10 20:40:19'),
(31, 5, 'win324567', 'Microsoft Windows 8.1, 64-Bit - OEM', '<div class="panel-content">\n<div class="product-info">\n<div>\n<p>With the new Windows, you can watch movies or play games, chat with friends, get work done with Office, access files anywhere or find your next favourite app in the Windows Store. And you can get to it all, including your familiar desktop, from the new Start screen.</p>\n<p>From the Start screen, you''re just a click away from the familiar Windows desktop you know, so you can do the same stuff you&rsquo;ve always done. Personalize your Start screen with your favourite news, friends, social networks and apps. Customizable colours and backgrounds and four different sizes of tiles make your Windows as unique as you are. Windows 8.1 gives you the power to quickly browse, watch movies, play games, polish your CV and put together a killer presentation &mdash; all on a single PC. Now you can organize up to three apps on your screen at once in a single view.</p>\n<p>In addition to great built-in apps for email, people, photos and video editing, you can also download thousands of popular apps from the Windows Store. Windows 8.1 works with different types of devices, including touch, mouse-and-keyboard, or both. Discover fast and fluid ways to switch between apps, move things around, and go smoothly from one place to another.</p>\n<p><strong>System Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Required processor: 1 GHz or faster</li>\n<li>Required memory: 2GB</li>\n<li>Required hard disk space: 20GB available</li>\n<li>Required video card: 1366 &times; 768 screen resolution; DirectX 9 graphics processor with WDDM driver</li>\n<li>Required connectivity: Internet access (fees may apply)</li>\n<li>Other system requirements: Microsoft account required for some features. Watching DVDs requires separate playback software.</li>\n<li>Additional system requirements: Some features such as touch may require a new PC. To check compatibility, visit the system requirements page at Windows.com. A TV tuner is required to play and record live TV in Windows Media Center. Free Internet TV content varies by geography, some content may require additional fees.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 103, NULL, 9, 'hcis6sycla_10978074-1405093952-226210.jpg', 1, 'hot', NULL, 'Microsoft Windows 8.1,Microsoft,Windows,64-Bit', 1, '2015-01-10 20:53:10'),
(32, 2, '432655', 'TomTom - VIA 1515M 5" GPS with Lifetime Map Updates - Black/Gray', '<div id="features">\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>Preloaded base maps</h4>\n<p>Include the U.S., Canada and Mexico with more than 10 million points of interest, 48 waypoints and lifetime map updates to help you reach your desired destinations.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>5" backlit touch screen</h4>\n<p>Makes it easy to navigate features.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>Text-to-speech and turn-by-turn voice prompts</h4>\n<p>Allow you to keep your eyes on the road while navigating with convenient voice guidance.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>Traffic and weather updates</h4>\n<p>Help you avoid traffic jams and weather delays.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>Advanced Lane Guidance</h4>\n<p>Provides precise directions.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>Built-in battery</h4>\n<p>Offers up to 3 hours of use per full charge.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>Automatic rerouting</h4>\n<p>For alternate travel directions in the event of a deviation from the directions given.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>Windshield mount</h4>\n<p>Along with an adhesive disk for dashboard mounting for flexible placement in your vehicle.</p>\n</div>\n</div>', 119, NULL, 0, 'p9sijjw15q_8767026_sa.jpg;canvasHeight=500;canvasWidth=500.jpg', 0, NULL, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S00zpn0Bfok', 'TomTom,1515M,GPS,TomTom - VIA 1515M,Map', 1, '2015-01-10 21:06:36'),
(33, 2, '432222', 'Magellan - RoadMate 2230T-LM 4.3" GPS with Lifetime Map Updates', '<div id="features">\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>Preloaded base maps of the U.S., Canada and Puerto Rico</h4>\n<p>With 7 million points of interest and thousands of waypoints for local navigation or traveling abroad.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>Backlit 4.3" color touch screen</h4>\n<p>Provides a large, bright display that is easy to see and control.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>Text-to-speech and voice prompts</h4>\n<p>Allow you to keep your eyes on the road while navigating with convenient voice guidance.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>Lifetime traffic alerts</h4>\n<p>Help you avoid possible traffic jams. Traffic camera alerts warn you of known red light and speed cameras during your trip.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>Lifetime map updates</h4>\n<p>Ensure accurate directions and up-to-date routes.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>Landmark guidance</h4>\n<p>Helps you locate your destination using landmarks.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>Best parking function</h4>\n<p>Offers parking garage locations, hours and directions, so you can easily find a convenient spot to park.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>Built-in rechargeable lithium-ion battery</h4>\n<p>With up to 2 hours of battery life.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>Automatic rerouting</h4>\n<p>Provides alternate travel directions in the event of a deviation from the directions given. Choice of route setup, auto sort multiple destinations and avoid highways/tolls mode help you customize your trip.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>microSD slot</h4>\n<p>Insert a removable media card (not included) containing additional map data or regional maps to expand your navigational ability.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<p>Lifetime Traffic is for the lifetime of the GPS Device or until Magellan no longer receives relevant traffic data, whichever is shorter. Lifetime Traffic may not be transferred to another Magellan device and may not be available in certain areas</p>\n</div>\n</div>', 129, NULL, 4, 'g0bz6bf8dk_5207942_500x500_sa.jpg;canvasHeight=500;canvasWidth=500.jpg', 1, 'new', NULL, 'Magellan,Map,2230T,RoadMate,GPS', 1, '2015-01-10 21:12:59'),
(34, 2, 'tom545677', 'TomTom - VIA 1605M RV 6', '<div id="features">\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>Preloaded base maps of U.S., Canada and Mexico</h4>\n<p>More than 7 million points of interest and up to 4 waypoints guide you toward interesting and useful destinations.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>Backlit 6" color touch-screen display</h4>\n<p>Offers a large viewing area and allows you to easily navigate settings in dim or bright lighting.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>Text-to-speech and turn-by-turn voice prompts</h4>\n<p>Let you keep your eyes on the road while navigating with convenient voice guidance.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>Split-screen junction view</h4>\n<p>Allows you to easily navigate unfamiliar exits.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>IQ Routes</h4>\n<p>Offer fast routes and accurate arrival times to help you plan your trip. Highway and toll avoidance makes it easy to select a preferred path to your destination.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>Oversize vehicle routing</h4>\n<p>Helps you find a route that is optimal for large vehicles.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>Built-in lithium-ion battery</h4>\n<p>With up to 3 hours of battery life.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>Automatic rerouting</h4>\n<p>Provides alternate travel directions in the event of a deviation from the directions given.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h4>microSD card slot</h4>\n<p>Insert a removable memory card (not included) containing additional map data or regional maps to expand your navigational ability.</p>\n</div>\n</div>', 200, 0, 5, 'aurgucuthu_9271063_sa.jpg;canvasHeight=500;canvasWidth=500.jpg', 1, 'hot', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mGPejx9lBZU', 'TomTom - VIA 1605M,TomTom,1605M,GPS,Map', 1, '2015-01-10 21:18:45'),
(35, 2, 'tom434323', 'TomTom - VIA 1435TM Automobile Portable GPS Navigator', '<div id="features">\n<div class="feature">\n<p>Navigation Instructions: Address Voice Control, Junction View, Lane Assist, Speed Assist, Text-to-Speech, Voice Command</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<p>Features: Bluetooth Hands-free, Emergency Help, High-sensitivity Receiver, Route Calculation</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<p>Memory Card Supported: Secure Digital (SD) Card</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<p>Flash Memory Capacity: 2 GB</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<p>Screen Size: 4.3"</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<p>Touchscreen: Yes</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<p>Bluetooth: Yes</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<p>USB: Yes</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<p>Form Factor: Mountable</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<p>Height: 3.1"</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<p>Width: 4.7"</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<p>Depth: 1"</p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<p>Weight (Approximate): 6.46 oz</p>\n</div>\n</div>', 115, NULL, 5, '6nhxq6lgle_1307707289_500x500_sa.jpg;canvasHeight=500;canvasWidth=500.jpg', 1, 'new', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mrJwN_ygV_g', 'TomTom,1435TM,Navigator,GPS,Automobile GPS Navigator', 1, '2015-01-10 21:23:46'),
(36, 5, 'ka234554', 'Kaspersky Internet Security 2013 - 3 Users 1 Year', '<div class="tab-overview-item">The Internet is filled with wonderful things, but there are some not-so-nice things out there as well. Kaspersky Internet Security 2013 works behind the scenes to protect you and your family against malware threats like viruses and spyware. It provides greater security for online shopping and helps to safeguard your digital identity. You can install it on up to three PCs.</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>More Information</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul style="list-style-type: disc;">\n<li>Uses real-time, proactive, and cloud technologies to provide protection against viruses, spyware, and other forms of malware</li>\n<li>Seeks out compromised programs to prevent them from damaging the rest of your computer</li>\n<li>Anti-phishing feature helps to protect your digital identity</li>\n<li>Two-way firewall blocks online attacks</li>\n<li>Safe Money and Secure Keyboard features help to secure your financial transactions for shopping, banking, and financial transactions through services like PayPal</li>\n<li>Parental control helps to protect your children by monitoring and limiting their activities, preventing the transfer of private data, and blocking harmful sites</li>\n<li>Controls applications in order to prevent dangerous ones from harming your computer</li>\n<li>Anti-spam feature filters out dangerous and unwanted emails</li>\n<li>URL Advisor adds colour-coded tags to web links, so you''ll know the danger level of the link you''re about to click on</li>\n<li>Works behind the scenes to update databases, check for the latest info about dangerous websites, and analyze program behaviour to protect your computer</li>\n<li>Optimized for maximum performance, so it won''t slow down your system</li>\n</ul>', 79, 0, 2, 'bzxhgo5kbd_10217322.jpg', 1, 'hot', NULL, 'Kaspersky,Internet Security 2013,Internet,Security,2013,licence,3 Users', 1, '2015-01-11 07:00:03'),
(38, 2, 'garmin123321', 'Garmin eTrex 20 2.2 Portable GPS', '<p>The Garmin eTrex 20 2.2" Portable GPS takes one of the most popular and reliable GPS handhelds and makes it better. Redesigned ergonomics, an easier-to-use interface, paperless geocaching and expanded mapping capabilities add up to serious improvements for an already legendary GPS handheld. The Garmin eTrex 20 2.2" Portable GPS is versatile and tough. And it''s built to handle whatever Mother Nature can dish out and more. With a 2.2" 65K color display, you can use this portable GPS navigation system even under bright sunlight. To offer precise direction, it is WAAS-enabled and also has HotFix satellite prediction. With an array of mounts, you can easily mount this Garmin eTrex GPS in your motorcycle.</p>\n<p><strong>Garmin eTrex 20 2.2" Portable GPS:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>The Garmin eTrex GPS has a 2.2" 65K color display - Sunlight readable</li>\n<li>Durable and waterproof - Withstands dust, dirt, humidity and water</li>\n<li>Array of mounts - Auto mount for turn-by-turn driving directions or rugged mount for motorcycles and ATVs</li>\n<li>Download GPX files and details to the unit for paperless geocaching - Stores and displays location, terrain, difficulty, hints, descriptions and more</li>\n<li>WAAS-enabled GPS receiver and HotFix satellite prediction - Get quick and precise locations</li>\n<li>The handheld GPS navigator tracks both GPS and GLONASS satellites simultaneously - Lock on to a position about 20 percent faster than with GPS alone, as well as the ability to lock on to 24 more satellites</li>\n<li>MicroSD card slot and 1.7GB internal memory - Load TOPO 24K maps, plug in BlueChart g2 preloaded cards, use the City Navigator NT map data or BirdsEye Satellite Imagery</li>\n</ul>', 158, 0, 12, 'z5itbgmj87_k2-_e65d03ee-32e7-4e29-afee-c12da7addcff.v1.jpg', 0, NULL, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lycL2ysjx1k', 'Garmin eTrex 20,Garmin,GPS,Portable navigation,navigator', 1, '2015-01-11 07:47:32'),
(37, 5, 'nor567889', 'Norton Security 2.0 - 5 Device, 1 Year', '<div class="tab-overview-item">Get peace of mind knowing that all your Mac and PC devices are safe, secure and protected. Norton Security connects you to proactive web protection, mobile device location, advanced privacy technology and more. Comprehensive coverage secures your favourite devices from smartphones to tablets.</div>\n<div class="tab-overview-item">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class="tab-overview-item">\n<p><strong>More Information</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>"Insight identifies PC files and applications that are safe or dangerous to identify incoming threats and proactively avert them</li>\n<li>SONAR Behavioural Protection detects signs that a PC file is dangerous in order to proactively protect you from new threats</li>\n<li>Safe Web for Facebook scans your Facebook Wall and News Feed for links to unsafe sites</li>\n<li>Always Up-to-Date automatically downloads and installs when you are not using your PC so important product and feature updates are ready when you are</li>\n<li>Download Insight prevents you from downloading files from websites that have a low reputation score within the Norton user community</li>\n<li>Insight + Optimized File Copy speeds up scan times by identifying safe files and only scanning unknown files</li>\n<li>Essential Online Protection helps keep your Mac safe from viruses, spyware and other threats, even if they come from PCs &ndash; without slowing it down</li>\n<li>Vulnerability Protection updates daily to defend against threats that can infect your Mac through gaps in the operating system or other applications</li>\n<li>Location Awareness lets you adjust your level of protection depending upon where you''re using your Mac &ndash; at home, the office, the local coffee shop or on the road</li>\n<li>Mac Application Controls allows you to control how your Mac applications connect to the Internet, who can connect to your Mac and what they can do and see</li>\n<li>Daily Protection Updates run in the background to protect your Mac from new, late-breaking threats</li>\n<li>Mobile Device Support protects multiple Android smartphones and tablets, as well as iPhones and iPads</li>\n<li>App Advisor powered by Norton Mobile Insight automatically checks and lets you remove Android apps and app updates that have potential privacy risks, intrusive behavior and high battery or data usage</li>\n<li>Anti-Malware powered by Norton Mobile Insight automatically scans downloaded Android apps and app updates for malicious apps and lets you remove them</li>\n<li>Remote Locate pinpoints your lost or stolen Android or iOS phone or tablet on a map to help you find it fast</li>\n<li>Lost Notice lets you send a customized message to anyone who finds your missing Android device, so you can make arrangements to get it back</li>\n<li>Sneak Peek uses the built-in webcam to take a photo of anyone using your Android device, using the front-facing camera once you list it lost or stolen</li>\n<li>Scream Alarm remotely sets off an alarm, so you can quickly locate your missing iPhones, iPads or Androids</li>\n<li>SD Card Scanning lets you automatically scan Secure Digital (SD) memory cards for threats when they''re plugged into an Android device</li>\n<li>Norton Community Watch collects information volunteered by millions of Norton users to spot new threats faster, identify safe files and provide stronger, more efficient protection for your PC, Mac, Apple or Android device"</li>\n</ul>\n</div>', 79.99, 0, 6, 'wapnk9bntd_10323618.jpg', 0, NULL, NULL, 'Norton Security 2.0,Norton,Security 2.0,Security', 1, '2015-01-11 07:01:19'),
(39, 2, 'garmin556702', 'Garmin nuvi 2757LM 7 GPS Unit with Free Lifetime Maps', '<p>The Garmin nuvi GPS, 2757LM model helps to ensure that you don''t get lost when you are on the road. It features a bright white backlit 7" display that is easy to see. The Garmin GPS Unit with Free Lifetime Maps of North America lets you quickly access millions of addresses and points of interest. For your convenience, you can save up to 1,000 waypoints, favorites and locations. The Garmin Auto GPS includes land assist, junction view and route avoidance to make travel easier. The rechargeable lithium ion battery can run for up to one hour before needing to be charged again. In addition to the Garmin nuvi GPS, 2727LM, you also get a USB cable, a vehicle suction cup mount and a quick start manual so that you have everything you need to get on the road.</p>\n<p><br /><strong>Garmin nuvi 2757LM 7" GPS Unit:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>800 x 480 pixels</li>\n<li>7" WQVGA color TFT with white backlight display</li>\n<li>Quickly access millions of addresses and points of interest with maps of North America</li>\n<li>Saves up to 1,000 waypoints, favorites or locations</li>\n<li>Compatible with micro SD cards (not included)</li>\n<li>Includes lane assist, junction view and route avoidance</li>\n<li>Rechargeable lithium ion battery</li>\n<li>Up to 1 hour battery life</li>\n<li>Includes: nuvi 2757LM, preloaded maps of North America, lifetime map updates, USB cable, vehicle suction cup mount and quick start manual</li>\n<li>Garmin GPS Unit with Free Lifetime Maps of North America is ideal for those who spend a lot of time on the road</li>\n</ul>', 189, 0, 5, 'mkeoglbg5d_k2-_95da0ea5-4af8-45fd-aa2c-7245e8e2c3a2.v1.jpg', 0, NULL, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vVjSOOganDE', 'Garmin,2757LM,GPS,map,navigation', 1, '2015-01-11 07:50:30'),
(40, 2, 'tom877732', 'TomTom GO 60 S 6 GPS with Lifetime Map and Traffic Updates', '<p>The TomTom GO 60 S 6" GPS Unit makes it easy to get where you''re going. Enjoy features like TomTom Traffic, 3D maps and Advanced Lane Guidance. Easily navigate through the menus on the included 6" touchscreen that benefits from a simple interface. Zoom in or out while navigating to get a better look at your route. Enjoy lifte-time free North American map updates for your TomTom Go GPS.</p>\n<p><br /><strong>TomTom GO 60 S 6" GPS with Lifetime Map and Traffic Updates :</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>6" touchscreen</li>\n<li>Lifetime North America map updates</li>\n<li>TomTom Traffic</li>\n<li>3D maps are included on this touchscreen GPS unit</li>\n<li>Advanced lane guidance</li>\n</ul>', 123, NULL, 7, 'raxpjbefin_k2-_8398bfe4-bc5c-4ff3-a3dd-2b1f96b02001.v1.jpg', 0, NULL, NULL, 'TomTom,GPS,Traffic Updates,Map,Navigator', 1, '2015-01-11 07:38:26'),
(41, 2, 'garmin563212', 'Garmin Oregon 600 3 GPS Unit', '<p>With its bright color TFT touchscreen display and many innovative functions, the Oregon 600 Garmin GPS Unit offers dependable and easy-to-use GPS mapping and positioning. This device offers a track log with 10,000 points and 200 saved tracks. The 3" handheld GPS unit has 4GB built-in memory for storage, and you can add more with the micro SD card slot. This item works with rechargeable or AA batteries for up to 16 hours. This Garmin GPS Unit, Oregon 600, also features dual orientation, advanced elevation plot, activity tracking and advanced waypoint management. The GPS system comes complete with a worldwide basemap, NiMH battery pack, USB cable for charging and carabiner clip.</p>\n<p><br /><strong>Garmin Oregon 600 3" GPS Unit:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>240 x 400 pixels</li>\n<li>3" transflective color TFT touchscreen</li>\n<li>Track log: 10,000 points, 200 saved tracks</li>\n<li>Portable GPS unit with 4GB built-in memory</li>\n<li>Compatible with micro SD cards (not included)</li>\n<li>Battery: Rechargeable NiMH pack (not included) or 2 AA batteries (not included)</li>\n<li>Up to 16 hours battery life</li>\n<li>Includes: Oregon 600, worldwide basemap, NiMH battery pack, USB cable for charging, carabiner clip and documentation</li>\n<li>Features: Dual orientation, flashlight, advanced elevation plot, activity tracking, advanced waypoint management and more</li>\n</ul>', 318.75, 300, 5, 'z1kosazuvn_k2-_80df5c8e-054e-43f8-b7b6-06ffd77bf7fc.v1.jpg', 1, 'sale', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LGfOY-YTBWc', 'Garmin,Garmin Oregon 600 3 GPS,GPS', 1, '2015-01-11 07:48:48'),
(42, 7, '567000', 'Canon Powershot G7X digital camera', '<div>\n<p>The Canon G7X Digital Camera is the newest, most efficient point and shoot on the market. This little powerhouse offers a large 1" 20.2 megapixel CMOS sensor. Paired with the DIGIC 6 Image Processor, this camera will be able to handle anything you throw at it. The 4.2x optical zoom range combined with a fast shutter speed and manual mode offers the user all the settings they need to make the image perfect each and every time. The f/1.8-f/2.8 lens also has Intelligent Image Stabilization which will reduce the visibility of camera shake in the final image. Another great benefit of the G7X is the full HD 1920 x 1080 video recording abilities in 60p, as well as the 6.5 fps continuous shootng rate. Sports and child photography are easy with the G7X, making this lens a wonderful choice for mothers or sports photographers of all skill levels. Last - but not least - to be mentioned is the built-in Wi-fi connectivity. The G7X has the ability to wirelessly transfer photos and videos to mobile phones, tablets, or computers. The addition of NFC (Near Field Communication) technology allows for easy connection with Android devices - simply by tapping the two devices together makes them connect. This mobile connectivity also allows for the user to remotely control the shutter release, operate the self-timer, flash, view images, and zoom from a distance.&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Megapixels:</strong>&nbsp;20.9 MP</li>\n<li><strong>Body Color:</strong>&nbsp;Black</li>\n<li><strong>Sensor Size/Type:</strong>&nbsp;1" / CMOS</li>\n<li><strong>Resolution:</strong>&nbsp;5472 x 3648</li>\n<li><strong>ISO:</strong>&nbsp;Auto, 125-12800</li>\n<li><strong>White Balance:</strong>&nbsp;Auto, Cloudy, Custom 1, Custom 2, Daylight, Flash, Fluorescent, Fluorescent H, Multi-Area White Balance, Shade, Tungsten, Underwater, White Balance Adjustment</li>\n<li><strong>Shooting Modes:</strong>&nbsp;Aperture Priority, Auto, Custom, Manual, Scene Modes, Shutter Priority</li>\n<li><strong>Image Stabilization:</strong>&nbsp;Optical</li>\n<li><strong>Optical Zoom:</strong>&nbsp;4.2x</li>\n<li><strong>Aperture Range:</strong>&nbsp;f/1.8-f/2.8</li>\n<li><strong>LCD Size:</strong>&nbsp;3" pivoting LCD touchscreen</li>\n<li><strong>Shutter Speed:</strong>&nbsp;1-1/2000 sec</li>\n<li><strong>Built-in Flash:</strong>&nbsp;Yes</li>\n<li><strong>Flash Modes:</strong> Auto, Flash on, Off, Slow sync</li>\n<li><strong>Continuous Drive:</strong>&nbsp;Up to 6.5 fps</li>\n<li><strong>Video:&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;Yes, NTSC</li>\n<li><strong>Memory Card Type(s):</strong>&nbsp;SD, SDHC, SDXC</li>\n<li><strong>Battery:</strong>&nbsp;1x NB-13L Rechargeable lithium ion battery pack (3.6VDC, 1250 mAh)</li>\n<li><strong>Weight:</strong>&nbsp;10.70 oz. / 303.3 g</li>\n<li><strong>Dimensions:</strong>&nbsp;4.1 x 2.4 x 1.6" / 104.1 x 61 x 40.6mm</li>\n<li><strong>Manufacturer''s Model #:</strong>&nbsp;9546B001</li>\n</ul>\n</div>', 698, 0, 5, '18zmm07ng6_1080917.jpg', 1, 'new', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N_1nCSEp8ok', 'Digital Camera,CANON POWERSHOT G7 X,G7X,CANON', 1, '2015-01-11 17:13:04');

